{
  "texts": [
    "Each platform required a unique method to extract the necessary content.",
    "For Facebook and Instagram, we employed CrowdTangle 50, a tool that offers social media analytics by tracking public content on different social media platforms.",
    "In the case of the Reddit dataset, we initially integrated the use of both CrowdTangle and Pushshift.",
    "However, we resort to Reddit dump after encountering issues with the Pushshift API.",
    "The Twitter dataset was compiled using its official API, prior to enforcement of rate alterations."
  ]
}